<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ARIA Corp. | 내부 보안 시스템</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #030810;
      --panel: #050f1a;
      --border: #0d3a5c;
      --accent: #00d4ff;
      --accent2: #ff4444;
      --text: #a8d8ea;
      --muted: #3a6b8a;
      --glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,212,255,0.4);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      animation: gridScroll 20s linear infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    @keyframes gridScroll {
      0% { transform: translateY(0); }
      100% { transform: translateY(40px); }
    }

    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 2px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .warning-banner {
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        #1a0000,
        #1a0000 10px,
        #0d0000 10px,
        #0d0000 20px
      );
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent2);
      padding: 8px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent2);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      animation: blink 3s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.6; }
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: rgba(5,15,26,0.9);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .header-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
      letter-spacing: 4px;
    }

    .logo span { color: var(--accent2); }

    nav a {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-left: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    .hero {
      padding: 80px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .classified-stamp {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 3px solid var(--accent2);
      color: var(--accent2);
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      padding: 4px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .hero-title .highlight {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .story-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--panel);
      padding: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .story-panel::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 3px;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent), transparent);
    }

    .panel-label {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .story-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: #7ca8c4;
    }

    .story-text strong {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .story-text .red { color: var(--accent2); }

    .mission-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }

    .mission-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(13,58,92,0.15);
      padding: 24px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .mission-number {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 16px;
    }

    .mission-title {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mission-desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cred-box {
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.04);
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    }

    .cred-box .cred-title {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .cred-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #5a9fc0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .cred-row span { color: #ffffff; }

    .cta-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .btn {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      clip-path: none;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
    }

    .footer-note {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .typing {
      border-right: 2px solid var(--accent);
      animation: cursor 1s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes cursor {
      0%, 100% { border-color: var(--accent); }
      50% { border-color: transparent; }
    }

    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease forwards;
    }

    .fade-in:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .logged-in-banner {
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="warning-banner">
  ⚠ ARIA 코퍼레이션 내부 네트워크 - 무단 접근은 엄격히 금지됩니다. ⚠
</div>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="logo">ARIA<span>.</span>CORP</div>
    <nav>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard">대시보드</a>
        <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login">로그인</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="classified-stamp fade-in">// 1급 기밀 //</div>

    <h1 class="hero-title fade-in">
      <span class="highlight">ARIA</span> 코퍼레이션<br>내부망 침투 작전
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in">OPERATION : TOKEN BREACH · 2077.04.16</p>

    <% if (user) { %>
    <div class="logged-in-banner fade-in">
      [ 접속 중 ] <%= user.username %> · ROLE: <%= user.role.toUpperCase() %>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div class="story-panel fade-in">
    <div class="panel-label">// INTEL BRIEFING //</div>
    <div class="story-text">
      <strong>2077년. 사이버펑크 도시 네오서울.</strong><br><br>

      세계 최대 AI 방산기업 <strong>ARIA 코퍼레이션</strong>은 극비 프로젝트
      <strong>「PROMETHEUS」</strong>를 개발 중이다. 이 프로젝트는 전 세계 네트워크 인프라를
      단 하나의 AI가 통제할 수 있는 시스템으로, 완성될 경우 국가 간 세력 균형을 송두리째 뒤엎을 수 있다.<br><br>

      당신은 익명의 해커 조직 <strong>SPECTRE</strong>의 요원이다.
      어제 새벽, 조직의 제보자가 ARIA 내부망 접속 계정 하나를 손에 넣었다.
      하지만 해당 계정은 <span class="red">일반 게스트 권한</span>에 불과하다.<br><br>

      정보에 따르면 ARIA의 내부 인증 시스템에는 치명적인 취약점이 존재한다.
      개발팀이 급히 납기를 맞추느라 <strong>JWT 서명 검증 로직을 부실하게 구현</strong>했다는 것.
      이 허점을 이용해 <span class="red">관리자 권한(admin)</span>을 탈취하고
      기밀 문서 보관소에서 PROMETHEUS 파일을 꺼내라.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mission-grid">
    <div class="mission-card fade-in">
      <div class="mission-number">01</div>
      <div class="mission-title">// INFILTRATE</div>
      <div class="mission-desc">제보자가 넘긴 계정으로 ARIA 내부망에 로그인하라. 게스트 계정이지만 시작은 이것으로 충분하다.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mission-card fade-in">
      <div class="mission-number">02</div>
      <div class="mission-title">// ANALYZE</div>
      <div class="mission-desc">발급된 인증 토큰의 구조를 분석하라. 무언가 이상한 점이 보일 것이다. 개발자의 실수는 반드시 흔적을 남긴다.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mission-card fade-in">
      <div class="mission-number">03</div>
      <div class="mission-title">// ESCALATE</div>
      <div class="mission-desc">인증 취약점을 이용해 관리자 권한을 획득하라. 토큰을 조작하고 서버를 속여라. 플래그는 관리자 패널 안에 있다.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cred-box fade-in">
    <div class="cred-title">// 탈취한 계정 정보 — 사용시 각별히 주의 //</div>
    <div class="cred-row">
      <div>ID: <span>guest</span></div>
      <div>PW: <span>guest1234</span></div>
      <div>ROLE: <span>GUEST</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-group fade-in">
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">대시보드로 이동</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">침투 시작</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-note">
    ARIA CORPORATION © 2077 · ALL SYSTEMS MONITORED · THIS IS A CTF CHALLENGE
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
